# Pricing Engine Rules

- Represent money using dedicated value objects/integers (minor units), never floating-point math.
- Apply pricing calculations deterministically with explicit rounding strategy.
- Version pricing rules when behavior may change over time.
- Keep tax/fee/discount composition order explicit and documented.
- Record enough metadata to reproduce final prices for audits/disputes.
